### HKDF Hierarchy

Domain-separated seed derivation ensures identical manifest → identical execution:

```rust
let global = B3Hash::hash(b"seed_material");
let router_seed = derive_seed(&global, "router");
let mut rng = ChaCha20Rng::from_seed(router_seed.try_into().unwrap());
```

**Why HKDF?** Cryptographically secure domain separation prevents cross-contamination between randomness sources (router, dropout, sampling, trainer, gate_noise, executor).

